SUMMARY:Time Well Spent Album Release Event
DESCRIPTION:Friday\, June 12 from 7-9pm\nLotus Firebay\nLocal indie folk band Time Well Spent is releasing their debut album Feel Change with a celebratory show at the Lotus Firebay on Friday\, June 12 from 7-9pm. Engineered by Lewis Rogers of Busman’s Holiday\, the album of original tunes written by Evan Copelly and David Lasuertmer will be played in its entirety with a 6-piece band\, and will feature opening act Pasha and the Poms.  \n$10 suggested cover.
URL:https://www.lotusfest.org/event/time-well-spent-album-release-event/
LOCATION:Lotus Firebay\, 105 S Rogers Street\, Bloomington\, IN\, 47404\, United States
CATEGORIES:Firebay Rental,Lotus Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.lotusfest.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/IMG_0294-1000.webp
END:VEVENT
