SUMMARY:Lotus on the Square
DESCRIPTION:Saturday\, October 3\n12:00 PM – 4:00 PM\nLotus at the Park is back…this time on the Square! Join us on Saturday\, October 3\, 2026\, from 12:00 PM – 4:00 PM for an afternoon of free\, family-friendly crafts\, activities\, and community fun in the heart of downtown. \nFamilies are invited to explore hands-on activities\, connect with local organizations\, and celebrate creativity together. Admission is free and all are welcome. \n\n		\n		\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				\n			\n		\n\nInterested in partnering with Lotus on the Square 2026?\nCommunity partners are invited to host a hands-on craft\, activity\, or interactive experience for kids and families. Or contact our production manager – Chaz Mottinger at productionmanager@lotusfest.org. \nApply Here
URL:https://www.lotusfest.org/event/lotus-on-the-square/
LOCATION:IN
CATEGORIES:Lotus Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.lotusfest.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/20220924_LITP_Switchyard-Park_Amanda-Hutchins.webp
END:VEVENT
